short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome DevTools extension for debugging Muban applications.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Allows you to display the Muban component tree inside the extension, and when clicking on each item, inspect its component-specific attributes, like props, refs and bindings.

Using inspection from both the web page and the extension allows you to easily select the desired component and view its information.

Most inspector properties are editable to allow you see how the component would be rendered if the values would change.
